  "1695000": {
    "name": "落虹之海",
    "steam_appid": 1695000,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/40a311b902f63aa629e9047dfb34b9f9.avif?t=1766366906\" width=620 height=350 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/083d326612837fb2bae1b81787ef15a6.avif?t=1766366906\" width=332 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >『落虹之海』取材自七福神的传说，是一部多结局互动声画读物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作品围绕被选为候补新神的「人类」以及拒绝与她交心的「七福神」展开，描写了他们为期一年的共同生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将在以像素风格呈现的宝船场景下探索触发剧情的要素，通过剧情当中的选项改变故事走向，从而抵达不同的结局。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事的结局共有22种，每一种都是真正的结局。通过串联起分布在各个结局当中的伏笔，可以拼凑出一幅只有玩家知晓的故事全貌。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/b75ff399ac9c88974dd2e9b532f0478b.poster.avif?t=1766366906\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/b75ff399ac9c88974dd2e9b532f0478b.webm?t=1766366906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/b75ff399ac9c88974dd2e9b532f0478b.mp4?t=1766366906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/fcd8defff182a26e337b371d89192d71.avif?t=1766366906\" width=332 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家需要在以像素风格呈现的宝船场景当中四处移动，与角色展开交流或调查各种物品，从而满足触发剧情的条件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >触发剧情的条件包括角色对主人公的好感度、天气、时间段等等。在剧情当中，可以通过各种选项让故事的走向发生变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现实中的1秒钟相当于游戏当中的1分钟，主人公的活动时间为6点至24点。无法保证充足的进食与睡眠将进一步缩短活动时间，请多加留意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一年后的新年第一天，游戏将根据触发过的剧情与角色的好感度抵达最终结局。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游玩一周目大致需要两小时左右。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/7e20d7848d10d1581fb663379ea4a91e.avif?t=1766366906\" width=332 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >睁开睡眼时，你身处一个只听得到阵阵浪花声的空房间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正在回忆自己为什么会来到这里，镜中的自己突然向你打起了招呼。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她叮嘱你要用谎言保护自己，然后就陷入了沉默。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/eb9652c31edcc503b88d6a53864d19c6.poster.avif?t=1766366906\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/eb9652c31edcc503b88d6a53864d19c6.webm?t=1766366906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/eb9652c31edcc503b88d6a53864d19c6.mp4?t=1766366906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >走出房间后，你遇到了一群自称七福神的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据其中一人——大黑天的说法，你是有幸被选为候补新神的人类。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于突然出现的你，大多数的福神似乎都并不欢迎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >距离宝船回到人间还有一年的时间，你究竟会成长为足以得到他们认可的新神，还是以原有的身份重回人间？又或是……？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从现在开始，你将与七福神共同度过梦幻般的一年。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/0425e27c4b541cff8818110333f0a98e.poster.avif?t=1766366906\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/0425e27c4b541cff8818110333f0a98e.webm?t=1766366906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/0425e27c4b541cff8818110333f0a98e.mp4?t=1766366906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/c9855f6deb373ff9554c27422b2ee7c3.avif?t=1766366906\" width=332 height=75 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/e0b76707c8561b5664e09128d9d9b92f.avif?t=1766366906\" width=798 height=248 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >擅长并喜好厨艺，大多数时间都花费在厨房里。其他的神也会在早中晚聚集到食堂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身为极具知名度的神祇却拥有平易近人的性格，因此成为了宝船上的中心人物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对主人公以及其他福神都非常关心，希望所有人都能和睦相处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/2a280da59aa71596734cb454ca2cefc8.avif?t=1766366906\" width=798 height=231 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >晴天时都会在甲板上钓鱼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与人类或其他神祇不愿发生过多交集，对主人公也十分冷淡，认为她只会带来麻烦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >似乎有些怕雨，会在雨天躲藏在书库里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/acb4d7de9d8180ae5f728c20e9fbe002.avif?t=1766366906\" width=798 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多才多艺的女神，钟爱水、音乐与学问。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逍遥自得地生活在不受其他人干涉的操舵室里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因其容貌被人类敬奉为爱与美的女神，却也兼具与武神相当的强大实力，可谓无所不能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更具备敏锐的洞察力，擅于掌握他人的特征。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/788e9a3dfb9b14d4651acf3fb6aae543.avif?t=1766366906\" width=798 height=265 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武神。平日里敦厚稳重，战斗时却会展现出冠绝八百万众神的强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不会说谎也不擅长识破谎言，更不能理解除自己以外的人为何说谎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很喜欢猫，但由于身材高大且不会摘掉铠甲与头盔，往往无法与之亲近。他本人也为此十分烦恼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/da04d170cbed49c1356b1c49c716f97e.avif?t=1766366906\" width=798 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >会用独特的口吻讲话。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于拥有预知未来的能力，时常透露出达观知命的态度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对与自己类似的人会怀有排斥感，但也不擅于应付心性过于淳厚之人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对茶与线香拥有独到的见解。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/e1351aa649ebe0b9bc700e12812e1778.avif?t=1766366906\" width=798 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时刻戴着狐狸面具，却不肯解释其理由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性格开朗，举止略显幼稚，但与其他福神同样远远年长于主人公。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在船上担任记录人类的阳寿与命运的职务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对现代的科学技术很感兴趣。每天都在船上四处闲逛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1695000/extras/2345f791576bd1a34c70e3c4fed38d8f.avif?t=1766366906\" width=798 height=211 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一天里绝大部分时间都守在书库，对所有书籍了如指掌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有少年般的相貌，言谈举止却处处显露着老练。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >性情温厚，在任何人面前都表现得泰然自若。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
